<li><a href="../../%e5%b7%a5%e7%a8%8b%e5%b1%82/%e6%90%9c%e7%b4%a2%e4%b8%8e%e6%8e%a8%e8%8d%90/ES%e8%bf%90%e7%bb%b4.md" rel="">ES运维问题</a></li>
<li><a href="../../%e5%9f%ba%e7%a1%80%e7%9f%a5%e8%af%86/%e7%bc%96%e7%a8%8b%e8%af%ad%e8%a8%80/jvm-internals.md" rel="">JVM原理</a></li>
</ul>]]></description></item><item><title>ES运维问题</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E4%B8%8E%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90/es%E8%BF%90%E7%BB%B4/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E4%B8%8E%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90/es%E8%BF%90%E7%BB%B4/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="es运维问题">ES运维问题</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：Elasticsearch运维的核心是平衡搜索性能、索引吞吐和集群稳定性，常见问题集中在磁盘不足、分片过多、内存压力大三个方面，通过索引生命周期管理、分片策略和监控告警体系来系统性解决。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="es运维围绕磁盘内存分片三个资源维度通过ilm和监控体系保障集群稳定">ES运维围绕磁盘、内存、分片三个资源维度，通过ILM和监控体系保障集群稳定</h2>
<h3 id="磁盘不足索引生命周期管理ilm">磁盘不足：索引生命周期管理（ILM）</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">索引生命周期：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Hot（热数据） → Warm（温数据） → Cold（冷数据） → Frozen（冻结） → Delete（删除）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   ↓               ↓               ↓                ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"> 高频搜索      只读，压缩存储   极少访问，慢查询   归档
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"> 高性能磁盘    普通磁盘          对象存储          低成本存储
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">ILM策略示例：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 创建后1天：进入Hot
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 7天后：进入Warm，缩小分片，forcemerge
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 30天后：进入Cold，关闭索引（只保留元数据）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 90天后：删除</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>磁盘优化措施</strong>：</p>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>措施</th>
          <th>效果</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>Force Merge</td>
          <td>合并段，减少文件数，降低磁盘占用</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>_shrink</td>
          <td>缩小索引分片数</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>关闭索引（Close）</td>
          <td>释放文件句柄，保留元数据</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>删除旧索引</td>
          <td>释放磁盘</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>压缩存储（best_compression）</td>
          <td>牺牲CPU换磁盘</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="分片策略避免过多或过少">分片策略：避免过多或过少</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>问题</th>
          <th>原因</th>
          <th>解决</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>分片过多</td>
          <td>每个分片有内存开销，元数据压力大</td>
          <td>合并索引，使用_shrink</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>分片过少</td>
          <td>无法利用多节点并行</td>
          <td>按30-50GB/分片预估</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>分片不均</td>
          <td>节点负载不均</td>
          <td>调整routing或rebalance</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<p><strong>分片数量建议</strong>：</p>]]></description></item><item><title>倒排索引</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E4%B8%8E%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95/%E5%80%92%E6%8E%92%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E4%B8%8E%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95/%E5%80%92%E6%8E%92%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="倒排索引">倒排索引</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：倒排索引将文档-词项的正向关系反转存储为词项-文档列表，使关键词查询从O(n)扫描降为O(1)查找，是搜索引擎和全文检索系统的核心数据结构。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="倒排索引将文档包含哪些词反转为词出现在哪些文档实现关键词快速定位">倒排索引将&quot;文档包含哪些词&quot;反转为&quot;词出现在哪些文档&quot;，实现关键词快速定位</h2>
<h3 id="核心结构词典--倒排列表">核心结构：词典 + 倒排列表</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">文档集合：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Doc1: &#34;Java is a programming language&#34;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Doc2: &#34;Python is also a programming language&#34;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Doc3: &#34;Java and Python are popular&#34;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">正向索引（文档 → 词）：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Doc1 → [Java, is, a, programming, language]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Doc2 → [Python, is, also, a, programming, language]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Doc3 → [Java, and, Python, are, popular]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">倒排索引（词 → 文档列表）：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Java         → [Doc1, Doc3]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Python       → [Doc2, Doc3]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">programming  → [Doc1, Doc2]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">language     → [Doc1, Doc2]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">is           → [Doc1, Doc2]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">popular      → [Doc3]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">...</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>倒排索引的存储结构</strong>：</p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>